TestNG - unit test Framework
TDD - Test Driven Development

Purpose - Design test cases in a systematic way
-- HTML reports
-- Different annotations
-- priorities can be set using TestNG 
-- Dependency 
-- grouping as there are 100 test cases
-- data provider feature

Test NG is an open source, Free - Its available in the form of Jar files

Its also called Java unit testing framework

Junit and TestNG is used with Java to design framework

Install TestNG in Eclipse